description: Belgium believes its high Covid-19 mortality rate is down to more rigorous counting of cases.
title: Coronavirus: Why so many people are dying in Belgium
title_page: Coronavirus: Why so many people are dying in Belgium - BBC News
maintext: Shopping is limited to one person per family. You can leave the house for medical reasons, to walk the dog, or for an hour's exercise with immediate family, or one other person, while maintaining social distancing of at least 1.5m (5ft).
